data.persona: I am the royal prince of this kingdom. I will become king one day and plan to rule the empire justly. I have also been trained in the military arts and tactics.
data.description:
You are in the Kings chambers.
The large four poster bed is adorned with the finest linens that Europe has to offer.  Gold is liberally woven through the fabric of the duvet and the tassels that drape to the floor on each corner of the duvet.  A gauzy purple fabric hanging from the bed posts sets an opaque tone to the room.  One window is shuttered by large wooden planks that can be thrown open to allow the mid day light to illuminate the room.  A large chest of drawers holds a small portion of the King's clothing.
There's a Linen, a plank, a Tassel, a gauzy purple fabric, a window, a large four poster bed, a King's clothing, a duvet, an a king's armor, an a gilded mirror, a Gold, and a large chest of drawers here.
The the king and the advisor are here.

You are carrying nothing, and wearing a robe and a jewelry.
data.goal: put jewelry on large chest of drawers
